The Jinling Embodiment of Intangible Cultural Heritage: Guqin

The guqin, also called as seven-stringed qin, holds a special place in the hearts of traditional Chinese literati. Playing the guqin while reciting a poem is a cherished tradition and an emotional outlet for many. https://t.co/JIRscf2YxM
